nip over after work, and far enough to feel like a proper treat when the gowns come out and the fizz is poured.</p>\n</div></section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "1eae64c", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "d01d836", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section class=\"section band-ivory2\"><div class=\"container split\">\n<div class=\"framed reveal\"><img alt=\"Veni Infantino floral appliqu\u00e9 bridal gown detail\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"__WTB_BASE__/assets/veni-1.webp\"/></div>\n<div class=\"reveal\"><span class=\"eyebrow\">Why Wigan Brides Come To Us</span><h2>200+ Gowns, Four Designer Houses</h2><span class=\"divider left\"></span><p>We're an official stockist of <strong>Sophia Tolli</strong>, <strong>Veni Infantino</strong>, <strong>Phoenix Gowns</strong> and <strong>White Rose</strong>, with over 200 gowns on the rails and dedicated plus-size collections. No rush, no rails to fight through \u2014 just space, time and honest advice to help you find the one.</p><div class=\"card-tags\"><span class=\"tag\">Private Appointments</span><span class=\"tag\">Plus Size Bridal</span><span class=\"tag\">Bridesmaids</span></div></div>\n</div></section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "53bca3d", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true},